{"tid":1995478,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"澳洲經驗 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-04-30T09:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T10:50:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8bb0113844897bac52e18d81e3fd6fe6582037","tid":1995478,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200430/20909423/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200430%2F20909423%2F&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=1081d7f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200430%2F20909423%2F&h=2db047fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200430/20909423/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲經驗 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200430/large/1588145901_bd21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200430%2Flarge%2F1588145901_bd21.jpg&h=50710ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府正研究分階段放寬因武漢肺炎而制訂的封閉措施，中、小學有望在短時間內開學。當然，所謂開學，並非全面重開，而是分階段開。比如每一天只允許每一個年級其中一個班開放，學生每星期輪流返校一天，減少人群聚集數目，以確保社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲是全球多個國家中疫情控制最好的國家之一，原因有。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重要原因則必須歸功於澳洲政府的果斷。武漢1月23號封關，澳洲2月1號禁止中國人及其他旅客從中國入境澳洲，這一隔中措施，比台灣還早了6天。源頭阻隔，有效控制疫情在澳洲擴散。<br />\n<br />\n一場武漢肺炎，每個國家都交出了不同的成績表，澳洲經驗值得借鏡。澳洲也是要求成立獨立調查小組，徹查疫症源頭及傳播途徑呼聲最高、態度最堅決的國家之一。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n我最關心的四個國家：加拿大、澳洲、日本、台灣之中，優柔寡斷、立場飄忽的加拿大和日本無疑損失嚴重。是時候認真檢討了。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"b0c18fae50084a678fac42cfb1d4d8c03e332012","tid":1995478,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"英倫三島罪人後代在這方面夠決絶，好似袓仙當年出走澳洲"}]}